{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"23ba4d64ea","title":"在延边自治州党委要求中央文革小组去电制止冲突报告上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3349c0fa4e","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":21,"articleId":"23ba4d64ea"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[{"id":"2850bfbd32","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"23ba4d64ea","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中共延边自治州委1967年1月19日给中央文化革命小组并东北局、吉林省委的这个报告说，18日下午3时，延边“无产阶级革命造反司令部”系统同延边“无产阶级革命造反大军”因为《延边日报》的接管问题发生武斗，已造成伤亡，规模很可能还会进一步扩大。州委三次派人到双方做工作，要求他们派出代表协商解决，均未成功。现在他们不信任州委，州委无法进行工作，事态发展又十分严重，急请中央文革给双方来电话或电报，制止冲突。"},{"id":"ee734ea02d","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"23ba4d64ea","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"总理，指周恩来。"},{"id":"e96fa6d74b","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"23ba4d64ea","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"毛远新，毛泽东的怪子，当时是“黑龙江省红色造反者革命委员会”的负责人。"}],"contents":[{"id":"45944f3b18","type":"title","text":"在延边自治州党委要求中央文革小组去电制止冲突报告“上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"23ba4d64ea"},{"id":"2850bfbd32","type":"paragraph","text":"总理","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"23ba4d64ea"},{"id":"ee734ea02d","type":"paragraph","text":"应当把延边反革命派手中的权力夺过来，请你部署一下。毛远新去延边工作一个月，那里大有起色。他今天去哈尔滨，如尚未走，可找他谈一下。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"23ba4d64ea"},{"id":"e96fa6d74b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"23ba4d64ea"},{"id":"a2338a1b18","type":"paragraph","text":"一月廿一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"